<p>This week a series of seemingly unrelated questions came in all with issues related to bad hardware&#8230; or at least seems so on the surface before your two favorite Mac Geeks dissect them and help get to the answer! Then John and Dave have some follow-ups from recent shows discussing screen sharing and DVD ripping. &nbsp;All this and more in episode 213! &nbsp;Subscribe today for free!</p>
